fields.description:
Define core types for the agent system.

## Deliverables
- src/agent/types.ts: AgentId, Complexity, ResolvedPolicy
- src/agent/status.ts: Status type, is_final(), status transitions

## Types
```typescript
type AgentId = string; // UUID

type Status =
  | { state: 'pending' }
  | { state: 'running' }
  | { state: 'completed', message?: string, structured_output?: unknown }
  | { state: 'failed', reason: string }
  | { state: 'shutdown' };

type Complexity = 'low' | 'medium' | 'high';

interface ResolvedPolicy {
  taskType: string;
  complexity: Complexity;
  model?: string;
  thinking?: ThinkingLevel;
  tools?: string[];
  skills: string[];
  sandbox?: SandboxConfig;
}
```

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] All types exported from src/agent/types.ts
- [ ] is_final(status) returns true for completed/failed/shutdown
- [ ] Status type matches codex AgentStatus semantics
- [ ] No runtime dependencies (pure type definitions)
